 the leattbrace® a revolutionary neck protection system for all helmeted sportsother patents and products are in development research and development takes place in cape town south africa and production is based predominantly in chinaleatt has warehouses and a distribution office in california for the north american market as well as a worldwide network of distributorslearn more about the company leatt historythe leatt story began in  when dr christopher leatt witnessed the death of a fellow motorcycle rider the weekend after his son matthew began ridingdr leatt began research and development of a device almost immediately driven by a passion to protect not only his son but all riders from the effects of catastrophic neck injuries his first patents were filed in learn more investor queriesdresner allen caron michael mason email michael mason  latest financialsleatt corporation first quarter  form qview pdf  download xbrlreleased  may leatt corporation  k annual reportview pdf  download xbrlreleased  mar leatt corporation third quarter  form qview pdf  download xbrlreleased  nov view all filings  financials navigationthe companyhomecompany profilemeet the teammission and strategyleatt historycode of ethicsleatt protectivesthe leatt blogleatt testimonialsinvestor infofilings  financialsstock quotesinvestor relationsshareholder presentationshareholder faqcontact usshareholder updates email signup notices  disclaimers   copyright leatt corporation     design by kriitcom contact informationresident agent pmb  b renaissance drive las vegas nv usa distribution office two eleven distribution llc  summit circle santa clarita ca office  toll free  fax head office  kiepersol crescent atlas gardens durbanville tel     fax     email investorinfoleattcom shareholder communication procedure the board of directors has established a procedure that enables stockholders to communicate in writing with members of the board any such communication should be addressed to michael mason email michaelmallencaroncom any such communication must state in a conspicuous manner that it is intended for distribution to the entire board of directors under the procedures established by the board upon the chairman of the boards receipt of such communication the companys secretary will send a copy of such communication to each member of the board identifying it as a communication received from a shareholder absent unusual circumstances at the next regularly scheduled meeting of the board held more than two days after such communication has been distributed the board will consider the substance of any such communication adsxy contact us  leatt corporation leatt corporation designers developers and marketers of innovative protective gear for sportsleatt corporationdesigners developers and marketers of innovative protective gear for sports contact us south african office kiepersol crescent atlas gardens business park contermanskloof road durbanville tel   fax   email investorinfoleattcom name email messagesolve    send a copy of this email to yourselfif you want to submit this form do not enter anything in this field navigationthe companyhomecompany profilemeet the teammission and strategyleatt historycode of ethicsleatt protectivesthe leatt blogleatt testimonialsinvestor infofilings  financialsstock quotesinvestor relationsshareholder presentationshareholder faqcontact usshareholder updates email signup notices  disclaimers   copyright leatt corporation     design by kriitcom contact informationresident agent pmb  b renaissance drive las vegas nv usa distribution office two eleven distribution llc  summit circle santa clarita ca office  toll free  fax head office  kiepersol crescent atlas gardens durbanville tel     fax     email investorinfoleattcom shareholder communication procedure the board of directors has established a procedure that enables stockholders to communicate in writing with members of the board any such communication should be addressed to michael m